</marc:datafield>
    <marc:datafield ind1=" " ind2=" " tag="500">
  <marc:subfield code="a">Layout:  Written in 25-26 long lines.  Vertical margins formed by folding.</marc:subfield>
</marc:datafield>
    <marc:datafield ind1=" " ind2=" " tag="500">
  <marc:subfield code="a">Script:  Written in German cursive script.</marc:subfield>
</marc:datafield>
    <marc:datafield ind1=" " ind2=" " tag="500">
  <marc:subfield code="a">Decoration:  11 watercolor illustrations of various explosives (f. 17v, 19v, 26v, 27r, 30r, 30v, 36r, 37v, 41v, 46r, 47r); sub-headings in red ink, with occasional headings and the first initial of the sub-headings in the same brown ink as the text; simple decorative elements in red ink at the end of some sections.</marc:subfield>
</marc:datafield>
    <marc:datafield ind1=" " ind2=" " tag="500">
  <marc:subfield code="a">Watermark:  Similar to Briquet, Armoiries - Salie&#x300;re 2177 (Geisenfeld (Bavaria), 1598).</marc:subfield>
</marc:datafield>
    <marc:datafield ind1=" " ind2=" " tag="500">
  <marc:subfield code="a">Binding:  Older spine with title in ink (Pulfer und Feuerwerke) laid on modern parchment binding.</marc:subfield>
</marc:datafield>
    <marc:datafield ind1=" " ind2=" " tag="500">
  <marc:subfield code="a">Origin:  Probably written in Bavaria or Austria, circa 1598 (watermark).</marc:subfield>
</marc:datafield>
    <marc:datafield ind1=" " ind2=" " tag="500">
  <marc:subfield code="a">Numerous leaves repaired in lower and outer margins, some with loss of text or image; some leaves partially torn along the fold marking the inner margin.</marc:subfield>
</marc:datafield>
    <marc:datafield ind1="0" ind2=" " tag="505">
  <marc:subfield code="a">1. f.1r-2r: Schwebell zuem Pulffer unnd Feuuerwercken zue Beraitten -- 2. f. 2v-3r: Schiess unnd Pu&#x308;chsenn Pulffer zue Machenn -- 3. f. 3v-56r: Rolenn zuem Pulffer unnd Feuuerwerckenn zue Beraitten -- 4. f. 56v-72v: Confortatinenn unnd Stoe&#x308;rkung zuem genug zumachen -- 5. f. 73r-85r: Volgt hernach ein gewisse [??eerr] wie man die grob unnd grossenn Stuck Ladenn Speisem unnd Richtenn solle -- 6. f. 85v-87v: Volgenn hernach die Articull unnd Privilegia der Pu&#x308;chsenmaister und Veldtherrenn -- 7. f. 88r-90r: Hernach volgenndte geschribenne Articull sein der Pu&#x308;chsenmaister Freihaittenn [??elhe] ein jeder Veldtherr denn Pu&#x308;chsenmaisteren zue haltten schuldig -- 8. f. 137v-178v: Ragettl[ei]nn.</marc:subfield>
</marc:datafield>
